      <h4 class="page-header punchline">
        Hadley Innovation is a scientific company specialized in weather insurance design. Our vision is to leverage the index market and to allow the 50 million smallholders farmers in sub-Saharan Africa to benefit from a cheap, transparent and tailor-made insurance product.
