      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="http://placehold.it/700x450" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 content">
        <p>
          Hadley Innovation proposes to overcome the challenge of missing information by simulating realistic rainfall data far from rain gauge stations. The simulator is inspired from state-of-the-art in geostatistics, peer-reviewed publications and uses acknowledged methods, classification tools and Markov chain model to resolve spatial and temporal rainfall variability.
        </p>
      </div>
  </div>

